ins*ert     [<ins>] ["<text>]           
2
n*ext,p*rev [n] ["<text>]               
2
del*ete     [<range>]                   
2
f*ind       /<str>[/[c][<range>]]       
2
s*ubst      /<str1>/<str2>[/[g][c][<range>]]
2
m*ove,c*opy [<range>] to <ins>          
2
join*l      [<range>]                   
2
